1.1.name: wordpress/recent-posts-embed
1.1.description: Recent Posts Embed is a plugin for Wordpress that allows you to easily place list of recent posts anywhere in your site. Recent Posts Embed is fully compatible with Wordpress 2.x and plays well with most other plugins.
